reviewText: Prompt delivery, was pleased with item, thank you
2 great events. Love the Spanish audio feature.

I received the order on time. I love watching fights. I used to like street fights but I no longer do. They are dangerous even for my eyes. UFC and other organizations have solidified the fight game for me. Thank you UFC and thank you Amazon. Because of BOTH of you, I am now the TRUE fight fan that I've always wanted to be!
